---
title: Asian Soy Beef & Ginger Rice Bowl with Sautéed Veggies & Sesame-Fried Eggs
description: This sizzling oyster sauce-infused beef bowl is a joy unparalleled. Simplicity is the winner here, with a topping of a sesame-fried egg and a squeeze of fresh lemon being the crowning glory on this quick and easy weeknight winner.

